==================================================
OPERATIONAL RISK ANALYSIS
==================================================

The platform should estimate:
“What happens if the contractor fails?”

LOW RISK:
- delayed office supplies

HIGH RISK:
- disrupted financial verification
- interrupted benefits processing
- operational outages

==================================================
SUBCONTRACT FEASIBILITY ENGINE
==================================================

For mission-critical systems:
The platform should determine whether:
- subcontracting is realistic
- subsystem contribution is realistic
- teaming opportunities exist

Examples:
Possible:
- dashboard subsystem
- analytics subsystem
- workflow tooling

Not realistic:
- replacing nationwide incumbent operational infrastructure directly

